            . I am a pawn broker. I had this waistcoat pledged with me on the 27th of August, I believe, by the prisoner, but cannot be positive,</p>
               <p>- Bradley. About two months ago I bought two white waistcoats of a man, who is, I believe, the prisoner at the bar.</p>
